Static Pods:
============

    - Kubelet check the definition files in /etc/kubernetes/manifests
    - Kubelet works at POD level
    - Pods that have no intervention from others is know as static Pods
    

Daemonsets vs Kube API Server
-----------------------------

Daemonsets                                              Kube API Server

Created by Kubelet                                      Created by Kube-API Server
Deploy control-plane components as                      Deploy Monitoring and Logging Agents on nodes
Static Pods

    Ignored by the Kube-scheduler
    
